      "locked": false,
      "text": "- Ability for users to upload files\n- Any file changes should be sync between\nusers devices. We can assume max 5\ndevices per user\n- Ability for users to share file with other\nusers\n- Support of different device types (web,\nmobile)\n\nOut of scope: upload images and videos",
      "fontSize": 19.860854541973005,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- Ability for users to upload files\n- Any file changes should be sync between users devices. We can assume max 5 devices per user\n- Ability for users to share file with other users\n- Support of different device types (web, mobile)\n\nOut of scope: upload images and videos",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "yuNg1Ma8_HXBwyHZft26r",
